---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Notifications from '../components/Notifications.astro';
---
<Layout title="Tentang Kami - TikTok Downloader">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 xl:px-12 2xl:px-16 py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 xl:py-20 2xl:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl xl:max-w-4xl 2xl:max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-3xl 2xl:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-center">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-2 sm:mr-3 lg:mr-3 xl:mr-3"></i>
          Tentang TikTok Downloader
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-white text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-lg xl:text-lg 2xl:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            TikTok Downloader adalah platform yang memungkinkan Anda untuk mengunduh video TikTok tanpa watermark dengan mudah dan cepat. 
            Kami menggunakan teknologi modern untuk memberikan pengalaman terbaik dalam mengunduh konten TikTok favorit Anda.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket mr-2 text-white"></i>
                Teknologi Modern
              </h3>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">
                Dibangun dengan Astro untuk frontend yang cepat, Hono untuk backend yang efisien, dan Bun sebagai runtime yang performant.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt mr-2 text-white"></i>
                Aman & Privat
              </h3>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">
                Kami tidak menyimpan data pribadi Anda. Semua proses download dilakukan secara real-time tanpa menyimpan file di server kami.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-center">Fitur Unggulan</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
          <div class="text-center p-4 sm:p-6 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-download text-black text-lg sm:text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Download Cepat</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Proses download yang cepat dan efisien tanpa batas waktu tunggu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 sm:p-6 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-search text-black text-lg sm:text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Pencarian Mudah</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Temukan video TikTok berdasarkan kata kunci yang Anda inginkan</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-4 sm:p-6 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-black text-lg sm:text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Responsif</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Bekerja sempurna di semua perangkat, desktop maupun mobile</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-center">Teknologi yang Digunakan</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
          <div class="text-center p-3 sm:p-4 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-2 sm:mb-3">üöÄ</div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Astro</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-xs sm:text-sm">Frontend framework yang cepat dan modern</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-3 sm:p-4 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-2 sm:mb-3">‚ö°</div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Hono</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-xs sm:text-sm">Backend framework yang ringan dan efisien</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-3 sm:p-4 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-2 sm:mb-3">üçû</div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Bun</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-xs sm:text-sm">Runtime JavaScript yang super cepat</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center p-3 sm:p-4 bg-black border border-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-2 sm:mb-3">üé®</div>
            <h4 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Tailwind CSS</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-xs sm:text-sm">Utility-first CSS framework</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black border border-white rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-center">Cara Menggunakan</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 sm:space-x-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Salin URL TikTok</h4>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Buka aplikasi TikTok dan salin URL video yang ingin Anda download</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 sm:space-x-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Paste URL</h4>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Paste URL tersebut ke dalam form download di halaman utama atau halaman download</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 sm:space-x-4">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-black font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-1 sm:mb-2">Download</h4>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base">Klik tombol download dan pilih format yang diinginkan (dengan atau tanpa watermark)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Notifications />
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      setTimeout(() => {
      }, 1000);
    });
  </script>
</Layout>